{"tid":1733182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非有嘢做，Call教護打民意戰","createTime":"2019-11-18T04:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T05:07:19.000Z","uid":52609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b47a5d316d4438358f5df14698215199865d50c5","tid":1733182,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:58:59.000Z","msg":"勇武繼續嘗試反包圍<br />\n和理非要打民意戰，參考621圍狗總招數<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【拍片煽情】</span></span></strong><br />\nPoly內有大量小朋友，和理非，普通宿生，教職員、大肚婆<br />\n警曱反口在Y-core出口圍困，完全無法離開校園<br />\n放上Twitter，國際戰線<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【Call 救護】</span></span></strong><br />\n由於被圍困，食物、水、醫療用品嚴重不足<br />\n有小朋友，和理非，普通宿生，教職員、大肚婆不舒服，即將有人員傷亡<br />\n集體CALL救護，用救護車開路<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">尖東救護站 2311 5111<br />\n何文田救護站 2624 6110<br />\n油麻地救護站 2770 2547</span></strong>"},{"pid":"01e492a5804bc31f7ea6a2b04d291af7b3cf1f12","tid":1733182,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"CALL爆救護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖東救護站 2311 5111<br />\n何文田救護站 2624 6110<br />\n油麻地救護站 2770 2547"},{"pid":"25c200f637150fa27c725da4e1020aade6136eda","tid":1733182,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ffd827161012e4caab56413419371b65c8e221","tid":1733182,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecc7656f6aaf8c7fdddc2f2c3bdc2ee9e43d28e","tid":1733182,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T05:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20dd057a263070192eaa701c95ba2d2b